<h2>Hello <%= clientName %>,</h2>

<p>
  You have received an invoice from 
  <strong><%= senderName %></strong> with the invoice code 
  <strong><%= invoiceCode %></strong>.
</p>

<p>
  Please review the invoice details in the attached PDF file.
</p>

<% if (paymentLink) { %>
  <p>
    For your convenience, you can click the link below to make an online payment:
  </p>

  <p>
    <a 
      href="<%= paymentLink %>" 
      target="_blank" 
      style="color: #2196F3; font-weight: bold;"
    >
      👉 Pay Now
    </a>
  </p>
<% } %>

<p>
  If you have any questions, please feel free to contact us via email or our support hotline.
</p>

<p>
  Best regards,<br />
  <strong><%= senderName %></strong>
</p>
